data.description:
1: Trump: The United States will impose a 10% across-the-board tariff on all imported goods;
2: Trump: Will impose 20% retaliatory tariffs on the EU country by country, and 24% tariffs on Japanese goods;
3: Fed Kugler: Tariff impact may be more lasting, supports standing still;
4: US congressman accuses Trump of wanting to replace the US dollar with personal stablecoins;
5: Arizona House Committee passes Bitcoin Reserve Act;
6: Arthur Hayes: If BTC can hold $76,500 until Tax Day on April 15, it will be "out of danger";
7: Justin Sun once supported the rescue of TrueUSD, but the stablecoin reserves are trapped in unauthorized illiquid investments;
8: Justin Sun: FDT is actually insolvent and unable to fulfill its obligation to redeem customer funds;
9: He Yi: Justin Sun is suing TUSD, not FDUSD;
10: First Digital: Justin Sun's accusation against FDT is false, and FDUSD reserves are safe and reliable;
11: PayPal Added support for SOL and LINK for users in the US market;
12: Retail giant 7-Eleven launches digital currency testing of the Bank of Korea;
13: Grayscale launches Bitcoin covered call option ETF and Bitcoin premium income ETF;
14: Alabama, USA, passed a bill allowing the state investment committee to allocate funds to BTC;
15: Binance starts the second round of voting for listings;
16: BNB Chain announced the first batch of 5 projects selected for the $100 million liquidity incentive plan, including Mubarak, TUT, etc.;
17: The number of ADP jobs in the United States in March was 155,000, the expected number was 115,000, and the previous value was 77,000;
18: 21Shares: It is most important for BTC to stay above the $80,000 range, and the impact of tariffs will soon become clear;
19: Bitfarms announced that it has signed a preliminary agreement for $300 million in private debt financing;
20: Wall Street first appeared to recommend investors to sell Strategy Analysts said that the market seems to be close to "saturation";
21: Trump Media Technology Group applied to issue 134 million shares of common stock and intends to apply to sell 8.4 million shares;
22: ARK Invest's ETF transferred 1,097 BTC to Coinbase, worth $94.06 million;
23: Cathie Wood's fund ARKK increased its holdings of more than 100,000 Robinhood shares;
24: Coinbase included RSR in the coin listing roadmap;
25: The giant whale deposited $5 million USDC to HyperLiquid to increase its holdings of HYPE, with a total floating loss of $1.3 million;
